{"tid":1056252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽巴士煲劇大聲播《皓蘭傳》不戴耳筒　車長開廣播KO：請調低電話音量","createTime":"2019-03-11T05:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T05:59:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cad0817a087d39aeb807cd611735f52bc033e972","tid":1056252,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2285000/2289621/bus20190310_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2285000%2F2289621%2Fbus20190310_600.jpg&h=d2606e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運輸署邀請影后Deanie姐葉德嫻拍短片mean爆無公德心的乘客，比如車廂內進食、開大手機聽音睇片、獨佔扶手柱等，但事實上無公德心的乘客依然不時見到。日前有網民乘搭九巴時遇到大媽車上睇《皓鑭傳》播片不戴耳筒，九巴車長於是開廣播，提乘客「調低電話聲量以免影響他人」，被一眾網民大讚「司機好嘢」！<br />\n<br />\n有網民在fb 群組「巴士的事討論區」發帖指，早前乘九巴290號往荃灣西總站，期間遇到一名大媽在車上煲劇，大大聲播《皓蘭傳》不戴耳筒，九巴車長即時廣播，提醒乘客要把手機音量收細。怎料在下一站，又有另一名大叔同樣大聲播片，網民稱：<br />\n搞到司機又要勸多次大家收細電話音量<br />\n<br />\n從網民上載的相片可見，車長於顯示牌亦特意提示乘客，要「調低電話聲量以免影響他人」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2285000/2289621/bus001_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2285000%2F2289621%2Fbus001_600.png&h=a6b4be6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少網民都大讚巴士車長「司機好嘢」，非常盡責，又分享每天上班下班時已非常疲勞，遇到大聲播片的大媽大叔真的很「勞氣」，連少少靜靜休息的時間都沒有。有網民更稱，巴士公司、港鐵應該考慮把葉德嫻為運輸署拍攝的宣傳片全日在車上播放。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2289621/大媽巴士煲劇大聲播《皓蘭傳》不戴耳筒%E3%80%80車長開廣播KO：請調低電話音量\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2289621%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E7%85%B2%E5%8A%87%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%B2%E6%92%AD%E3%80%8A%E7%9A%93%E8%98%AD%E5%82%B3%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%B4%E8%80%B3%E7%AD%92%25E3%2580%2580%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E9%96%8B%E5%BB%A3%E6%92%ADKO%EF%BC%9A%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E4%BD%8E%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E9%9F%B3%E9%87%8F&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=bcebe8c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2289621/大媽巴士煲劇大聲播《皓蘭傳》不戴耳筒%E3%80%80車長開廣播KO：請調低電話音量</a>"},{"pid":"ccdb660ba1122d28ed067f59029ac981e0df1a54","tid":1056252,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚憎啲開speaker 嘈住人嘅陷家剷"},{"pid":"a18d9770b67d601713902e57c8dbe14db44fe277","tid":1056252,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a7ca92cc4e6526b7bbda553f4f100cda75e017","tid":1056252,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"呢啲短命種冚家剷<br />\n<br />\n應該搵部機喺佢耳邊播，睇佢收唔收皮。"},{"pid":"9d109fc56a221972bdfdf2645115b1e56e625545","tid":1056252,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"支那婆/廢中：咁撚巴閉，坐的士囉！"},{"pid":"353425406d591356460484fd97de3768d45628d9","tid":1056252,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccdb660ba1122d28ed067f59029ac981e0df1a54","tid":1056252,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚憎啲開speaker 嘈住人嘅陷家剷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"特別返工放工時間嘈到想訓都訓唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc93ae7d68409a0846d6190160554e2dce0359a","tid":1056252,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353425406d591356460484fd97de3768d45628d9","tid":1056252,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ccdb660ba1122d28ed067f59029ac981e0df1a54","tid":1056252,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:26:16.000Z